title: Unger's Win Not Enough as Blue Devils Fall at No. 10 Virginia Tech - Duke University - GoDuke.com
content: Unger's Win Not Enough as Blue Devils Fall at No. 10 Virginia Tech - Duke University  GoDuke.com
description: The Duke wrestling program (6-8, 0-3 ACC) dropped a 42-3 decision to No. 10 Virginia Tech (7-3, 2-1 ACC) on Friday night at Cassell Coliseum.
